ary 12]] \u2013 [[David D. Friedman]], American economist\n* [[February 14]] \u2013 [[Carl Bernstein]], American investigative journalist and author\n* [[February 15]] \u2013 [[Douglas Hofstadter]], American cognitive scientist\n* [[February 17]] \u2013 [[Zina Bethune]], American actress, dancer and choreographer (d. [[2012 in the United States|2012]])\n* [[February 20]] \u2013 [[Henry Polic II]], American actor (d. [[2013]])\n* [[February 22]] \u2013 [[Oliver (singer)|Oliver]], American singer (''[[Good Morning Starshine]]'') (d. [[2000]])\n* [[February 24]] \u2013 [[Barry Bostwick]], American actor\n* [[February 25]] \u2013 [[Roy Saari]], American swimmer (d. [[2008]])\n* [[February 27]] \u2013 [[Carl Anderson (singer)|Carl Anderson]], American singer, actor (''[[Jesus Christ Superstar]]'') (d. [[2004]])\n* [[February 28]] \u2013 [[Bubba Smith]], American football player, actor (d. [[2011]])\n\n===March===\n[[File:Micky Dolenz at the 2009 Tribeca Film Festival.jpg|thumb|100px|[[Micky Dolenz]]]]\n[[File:Charles Greene 1970.jpg|thumb|100px|[[Charles Greene (athlete)|Charles Greene]]]]\n* [[March 1]] \u2013 [[Dirk Benedict]], American actor\n* [[March 2]] \u2013 [[Joy Garrett]], American actor and vocalist (d. [[1993 in the United States|1993]])\n* [[March 3]] \u2013 [[Hattie Winston]], American actress\n* [[March 4]] \u2013 [[Gary Williams (basketball)|Gary Williams]], American basketball coach\n* [[March 7]] \u2013 [[Arthur Lee (musician)|Arthur Lee]], American musician (d. [[2006]])\n* [[March 8]]\n** [[Jim Chapman (congressman)|Jim Chapman]], American politician\n** [[Micky Dolenz]], American actor, director and rock musician (''[[The Monkees]]'')\n* [[March 9]] \u2013 [[Dennis Rader]], American serial killer\n* [[March 12]] \u2013 [[Sammy Gravano]], American mobster\n* [[March 14]]\n** [[Michael Martin Murphey]], American singer-songwriter and guitarist\n** [[Walter Parazaider]], American saxophonist ([[Chicago (band)|Chicago]])\n* [[March 20]]\n** [[Bobby James