tteMidler90cropped.jpg|thumb|100px|[[Bette Midler]]]]\n[[File:Ernie Hudson by Gage Skidmore 2.jpg|thumb|100px|[[Ernie Hudson]]]]\n[[File:Diane Sawyer 2011 Shankbone.JPG|thumb|100px|[[Diane Sawyer]]]]\n* [[December 1]] \u2013 [[Bette Midler]], American actress and singer<ref>{{cite web |title=Bette Midler {{!}} Biography, Music, Movies, & Facts |url=https://www.britannica.com/biography/Bette-Midler |website=Encyclopedia Britannica |accessdate=23 October 2019 |language=en}}</ref>\n* [[December 2]] \u2013 [[Charles \"Tex\" Watson]], American prisoner, 'Manson Family' member\n* [[December 6]] \u2013 [[Larry Bowa]], American baseball player, manager\n* [[December 9]] \u2013 [[Michael Nouri]], American actor\n* [[December 13]]\n** [[Herman Cain]], African-American politician, author, business executive, radio host, syndicated columnist, and Tea Party activist\n** [[Kathy Garver]], American actress, author and online radio hostess\n** [[Heather North]], American actress (d. [[2017]])\n* [[December 16]] \u2013 [[Patti Deutsch]], American voice actress (d. [[2017]])\n* [[December 17]]\n** [[Ernie Hudson]], African-American actor\n** [[Chris Matthews]], American news anchor\n* [[December 18]] \u2013 [[Carolyn Wood (swimmer)|Carolyn Wood]], American professional swimmer \n* [[December 19]] \u2013 [[Elaine Joyce]], American actress, game show panelist\n* [[December 20]]\n** [[Bruce Baker (geneticist)|Bruce Baker]], American geneticist (d. [[2018]])\n** [[Peter Criss]], American rock drummer (''[[Kiss (band)|KISS]]'') \n* [[December 22]]\n** [[Diane Sawyer]], American news journalist\n** [[T. K. Wetherell]], American politician, educator (d. [[2018]])\n* [[December 23]] \u2013 [[Donald A. Ritchie]], American historian\n* [[December 24]] \u2013 [[Nicholas Meyer]], American screenwriter, producer, director and novelist\n* [[December 25]] \u2013 [[Gary Sandy]], American actor \n* [[December 26]] \u2013 [[John Walsh (television host)|John Walsh]], American media personality (''[[Ame